Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.rfidscanner

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RFIDScannerInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the RFIDScanner device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DisableTag
    Output request executor for RFIDScanner method DisableTag.
    Factory
    General part of RFIDScanner factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    LockTag
    Output request executor for RFIDScanner method LockTag.
    ReadTags
    Input request executor for RFIDScanner method ReadTags and StartReadTags.
    RFIDRequest
    Base class for output request executor for RFIDScanner method DisableTag, LockTag, WriteTagData and WriteTagID.
    RFIDScannerDataEvent
    Data event implementation for RFIDScanner devices.
    RFIDScannerErrorEvent
    Error event implementation for RFIDScanner devices.
    RFIDScannerProperties
    Class containing the RFID scanner specific properties, their default values and default implementations of RFIDScannerInterface.
    RFIDScannerService
    RFIDScanner service implementation.
    RFIDScannerTagData
    Helper class for RFIDScanner tag data.
    StartReadTags
    Input request executor for RFIDScanner method ReadTags and StartReadTags.
    WriteTagData
    Output request executor for RFIDScanner method WriteTagData.
    WriteTagID
    Output request executor for RFIDScanner method WriteTagID.
